    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and runs like a charm! It's perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
