    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This unit delivers a linear power curve up to an 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The chassis maintains excellent lateral rigidity thanks to proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The drivetrain is rounded out by a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution across the rear axle. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul. While the aesthetic condition is consistent with a well-loved driver's car, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression across all cylinders\u2014remain within factory specifications. This is a purist-spec M-car optimized for throttle response and steering feedback.",
